WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'Iarrow' is a Workbench game that is based on the popular
sliding-tile-puzzle but with a little twist: you have to move or
rotate arrows in order to 'move' an empty space from the upper
left to the lower right area of the game board. Do this in the
fewest moves possible.

  As you move or rotate arrows, other arrows randomly rotate just
to complicate the gameplay a little...

  Have fun!

FEATURES
--------

  -Simple installation: just run the game and play!

  -5 game board sizes to play with: from a 4 by 4 tile size to an
   8 by 8 tile size.

  -Small package, the Lha archive is smaller than 50K, so it
   doesn't take ages to download :)

  -The game plays on the Workbench screen and its window is
   resizeable.

